    <div class="content-section introduction">
        <div class="feature-intro">
            <h1>FlexGrid</h1>
            <p>
                Flex Grid CSS is a lightweight flex based responsive layout utility optimized for mobile phones, tablets and desktops.
                Flex Grid CSS is not included in PrimeReact as it is provided by <a href="https://github.com/primefaces/primeflex">PrimeFlex</a> ,  a shared grid library between PrimeFaces, PrimeNG, PrimeReact and PrimeVue projects.
            </p>
